      "schemeDefinitions": [],
      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Only 2 sons/daughters of registered sanitation workers are eligible for the scholarship.\n1. The scholarship is provided for studying different courses.\n1. After admission in college/polytechnic or other course for engineering or medical education, the students receiving scholarship amount under this scheme but student must study for minimum one year in that course.\n1. If such a student is eligible to receive scholarship amount under any scheme of any other government department/institution, then he/she can choose any one scheme which is beneficial for him/her.\n1. The student cannot avail benefits of two schemes simultaneously.\n\n",
